# Setup Steps

## 1. Virtual Machine Creation
Created the following virtual machines in Oracle VirtualBox:
- Ubuntu Server LTS
- Windows Server 2022
- Kali Linux


## 2. Network Configuration
Configured:
- NAT adapter for internet access
- Host-Only adapter for internal communication


## 3. Wazuh Installation
Installed Wazuh on Ubuntu Server using the official installation script.

Commands used:
in bash : curl -sO https://packages.wazuh.com/4.7/wazuh-install.sh
in bash : sudo bash wazuh-install.sh -a
